# Rust
/target
**/target/
**/*.rs.bk
# Cargo.lock IS committed: gearbox ships a binary, and a pinned lockfile is required for
# reproducible/auditable builds and meaningful `cargo audit` / `cargo deny` in CI.

# Python
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
.venv/

# Signing keys / secrets — never commit
*.key
*.pem
secrets/
.env
.env.*

# Generated catalogs / artifacts (build output)
/dist
/out
*.app-registry.json

# OS / editor
.DS_Store
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
